View.Name: PostDeploymentHealthSurvey
View.CheckCode:
DefineVariables DEFINE ERHMS NETOBJECT "ERHMS Info Manager.Integration" DEFINE WorkerId TEXTINPUT End-DefineVariables
Field WorkerInfo_GetGlobalRecordId Click ASSIGN WorkerId = ERHMS.GetWorkerId(WorkerInfo_FirstName, WorkerInfo_LastName, WorkerInfo_EmailAddress, WorkerInfo_GlobalRecordId) IF WorkerId <> "" THEN ASSIGN WorkerInfo_GlobalRecordId = WorkerId END-IF End-Click End-Field

Field.Name: CurrentHealthAbsolute
Field.PromptText: How would you rate your current health?

Field.Name: CurrentHealthRelative
Field.PromptText: How would you rate your current health, compared to before this deployment?

Field.Name: HasSymptoms
Field.PromptText: Have you experienced any symptoms of illness since returning from this deployment?

Field.Name: SymptomsSkipLabel
Field.PromptText: If not, skip the rest of this section.

Field.Name: Symptoms
Field.PromptText: What symptoms have you experienced? Check all that apply.

Field.Name: ReceivedMedicalTreatment
Field.PromptText: Have you received medical treatment for these symptoms?

Field.Name: IsUsingTobacco
Field.PromptText: Have you smoked cigarettes or used other tobacco products since returning from this deployment?

Field.Name: TobaccoUseSkipLabel
Field.PromptText: If not, skip the rest of this section.

Field.Name: TobaccoUseRelative
Field.PromptText: Are you smoking/using more or less than before this deployment?

Field.Name: IsDrinkingAlcohol
Field.PromptText: Have you drunk alcohol since returning from this deployment?

Field.Name: AlcoholUseSkipLabel
Field.PromptText: If not, skip the rest of this section.

Field.Name: AlcoholUseRelative
Field.PromptText: Are you drinking more or less than before this deployment?

Field.Name: Concerns
Field.PromptText: What other health concerns do you have related to this deployment?
